                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT1473GadlaL"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><note>A rhymed prologue</note><locus from="1ra" to="1vb"></locus>        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፨ በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ ዘአምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡ ህላዌሁ፨
                              ወእስከ፡ ለዓለም፡ ዘኢየሐልቅ፡ ምስፍናሁ። ልዑል፡ በልዕልናሁ፨ ስብሕ፡ በስብሐቲሁ፨ ...</incipit>
                        <note>The text seems closer to the text as in the so-called <title ref="LIT7616GadLib2">second recension</title>, but with some more
                           passages in the initial part.</note>
